Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.61,0:00:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.48,0:00:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我是赞州中学勇者部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.10,0:00:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者 结城友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.91,0:00:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,给我传达到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.00,0:00:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你要活下去…
